%package apidocs
Summary:	API documentation for ModemManager
Summary(pl.UTF-8):	Dokumentacja API ModemManagera
Group:		Documentation
Requires:	gtk-doc-common

%description apidocs
API documentation for ModemManager.

%description apidocs -l pl.UTF-8
